### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/health

### Frontend-compatible data
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/data

### Open tasks
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tasks/open

### Suggested matches for a need
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tasks/N-1042/matches

### Create a new community need
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/needs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Food / Nutrition",
  "severity": "High",
  "location": "Dharavi",
  "description": "Families need cooked meals and dry ration kits.",
  "peopleAffected": 120,
  "reportedBy": "Field Team Beta"
}

### Register a volunteer
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/volunteers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Neha Rao",
  "skills": ["Logistics", "Driving"],
  "location": "Kurla West",
  "availability": "Available Now",
  "languages": ["Hindi", "English"],
  "reliabilityScore": 90
}

### Assign a volunteer to a need
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "needId": "N-1042",
  "volunteerId": "V-002",
  "assignedBy": "Program Manager"
}

### Analytics
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analytics

### Notifications
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications

### Mark notification as read
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications/NT-1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isRead": true
}
